What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Spouted Pouches Market?

Spouted Pouches Market Analysis and Size

The spouted pouches market is witnessing significant growth, driven by increasing demand for convenient and sustainable packaging solutions across various industries. Spouted pouches offer advantages such as ease of use, portability, and reduced material usage compared to traditional packaging formats. The food and beverage sector is a major market driver, with applications in baby food, sauces, and beverages. In addition, the cosmetics and personal care industry is adopting spouted pouches for items such as shampoos and lotions. The market also benefits from technological advancements, such as improved barrier properties and innovative designs.

The global spouted pouches market size was valued at USD 3.54 billion in 2023 and is projected to reach USD 7.05 billion by 2031, with a CAGR of 9% during the forecast period of 2024 to 2031. In addition to the insights on market scenarios such as market value, growth rate, segmentation, geographical coverage, and major players, the market reports curated by the Data Bridge Market Research also include in-depth expert analysis, geographically represented company-wise production and capacity, network layouts of distributors and partners, detailed and updated price trend analysis and deficit analysis of supply chain and demand.

